Conflicts: insync-dolphin
Replaces: insync-dolphin
Description: Insync context menus and overlay icons for Dolphin (Plasma 6)
 This plugin adds Insync integration to the Dolphin file manager
 on KDE Plasma 6. It provides context menu actions (Add to Insync,
 Share, etc.) and file overlay status icons (synced, syncing, error).
